<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Asking<sp/>a<sp/>question</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Questions<sp/>about<sp/>how<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>GLFW<sp/>should<sp/>be<sp/>asked<sp/>either<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>[support</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">section](https://discourse.glfw.org/c/support)<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>forum,<sp/>under<sp/>the<sp/>[Stack</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Overflow<sp/>tag](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/glfw)<sp/>or<sp/>[Game</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Development<sp/>tag](https://gamedev.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/glfw)<sp/>on</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Stack<sp/>Exchange<sp/>or<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>IRC<sp/>channel<sp/>`#glfw`<sp/>on</highlight></codeline>
