<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Questions<sp/>about<sp/>the<sp/>design<sp/>or<sp/>implementation<sp/>of<sp/>GLFW<sp/>or<sp/>about<sp/>future<sp/>plans</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">should<sp/>be<sp/>asked<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>[dev<sp/>section](https://discourse.glfw.org/c/dev)<sp/>of<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">forum<sp/>or<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>IRC<sp/>channel.<sp/><sp/>Please<sp/>don&apos;t<sp/>open<sp/>a<sp/>GitHub<sp/>issue<sp/>to<sp/>discuss<sp/>design</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">questions<sp/>without<sp/>first<sp/>checking<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>maintainer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
