<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Reporting<sp/>a<sp/>context<sp/>creation<sp/>bug</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">__Note:__<sp/>Windows<sp/>ships<sp/>with<sp/>graphics<sp/>drivers<sp/>that<sp/>do<sp/>not<sp/>support<sp/>OpenGL.<sp/><sp/>If</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">GLFW<sp/>says<sp/>that<sp/>your<sp/>machine<sp/>lacks<sp/>support<sp/>for<sp/>OpenGL,<sp/>it<sp/>very<sp/>likely<sp/>does.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Install<sp/>drivers<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>computer<sp/>manufacturer<sp/>or<sp/>graphics<sp/>card<sp/>manufacturer</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">([Nvidia](https://www.geforce.com/drivers),</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">[AMD](https://www.amd.com/en/support),</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">[Intel](https://www-ssl.intel.com/content/www/us/en/support/detect.html))<sp/>to</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">fix<sp/>this.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">__Note:__<sp/>AMD<sp/>only<sp/>supports<sp/>OpenGL<sp/>ES<sp/>on<sp/>Windows<sp/>via<sp/>EGL.<sp/><sp/>See<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">[GLFW\_CONTEXT\_CREATION\_API](https://www.glfw.org/docs/latest/window_guide.html#window_hints_ctx)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">hint<sp/>for<sp/>how<sp/>to<sp/>select<sp/>EGL.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
