<codeline><highlight class="normal">reporting<sp/>it<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>bug.<sp/><sp/>This<sp/>tool<sp/>is<sp/>included<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>GLFW<sp/>source<sp/>tree<sp/>as</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">`tests/glfwinfo.c`<sp/>and<sp/>is<sp/>built<sp/>along<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>library.<sp/><sp/>It<sp/>has<sp/>switches<sp/>for<sp/>all</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">GLFW<sp/>context<sp/>and<sp/>framebuffer<sp/>hints.<sp/><sp/>Run<sp/>`glfwinfo<sp/>-h`<sp/>for<sp/>a<sp/>complete<sp/>list.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Always<sp/>include<sp/>the<sp/>__operating<sp/>system<sp/>name<sp/>and<sp/>version__<sp/>(e.g.<sp/>`Windows</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">7<sp/>64-bit`<sp/>or<sp/>`Ubuntu<sp/>15.10`).<sp/><sp/>If<sp/>you<sp/>are<sp/>using<sp/>an<sp/>official<sp/>release<sp/>of<sp/>GLFW,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">include<sp/>the<sp/>__GLFW<sp/>release<sp/>version__<sp/>(e.g.<sp/>`3.1.2`),<sp/>otherwise<sp/>include<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">__GLFW<sp/>commit<sp/>ID__<sp/>(e.g.<sp/><sp/>`3795d78b14ef06008889cc422a1fb8d642597751`)<sp/>from<sp/>Git.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">If<sp/>you<sp/>are<sp/>running<sp/>your<sp/>program<sp/>in<sp/>a<sp/>virtual<sp/>machine,<sp/>please<sp/>mention<sp/>this<sp/>and</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">include<sp/>the<sp/>__VM<sp/>name<sp/>and<sp/>version__<sp/>(e.g.<sp/>`VirtualBox<sp/>5.1`).</highlight></codeline>
