<codeline><highlight class="normal">__GPU<sp/>model<sp/>and<sp/>driver<sp/>version__<sp/>(e.g.<sp/>`GeForce<sp/>GTX660<sp/>with<sp/>352.79`),<sp/>and<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
