<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Reporting<sp/>a<sp/>monitor<sp/>or<sp/>video<sp/>mode<sp/>bug</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">__Note:__<sp/>On<sp/>headless<sp/>systems<sp/>on<sp/>some<sp/>platforms,<sp/>no<sp/>monitors<sp/>are<sp/>reported.<sp/><sp/>This</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">causes<sp/>glfwGetPrimaryMonitor<sp/>to<sp/>return<sp/>`NULL`,<sp/>which<sp/>not<sp/>all<sp/>applications<sp/>are</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">prepared<sp/>for.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">__Note:__<sp/>Some<sp/>third-party<sp/>tools<sp/>report<sp/>more<sp/>video<sp/>modes<sp/>than<sp/>are<sp/>approved<sp/>of</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">by<sp/>the<sp/>OS.<sp/><sp/>For<sp/>safety<sp/>and<sp/>compatibility,<sp/>GLFW<sp/>only<sp/>reports<sp/>video<sp/>modes<sp/>the<sp/>OS</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">wants<sp/>programs<sp/>to<sp/>use.<sp/><sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>a<sp/>bug.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>`monitors`<sp/>tool<sp/>is<sp/>included<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>GLFW<sp/>source<sp/>tree<sp/>as<sp/>`tests/monitors.c`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">and<sp/>is<sp/>built<sp/>along<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>library.<sp/><sp/>It<sp/>lists<sp/>all<sp/>information<sp/>GLFW<sp/>provides</highlight></codeline>
